&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot; line=&quot;oCh5&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;主题分享  《&lt;strong&gt;人工智能在基因工程领域的应用&lt;/strong&gt;》 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
